trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar `Dispose` quando tiver terminado de utilizando <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O `Dispose` método mantém o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>num Estado não utilizável.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Após a chamada `Dispose`, tem de libertar todas as referências ao <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>para que o recoletor de lixo pode reclame a memória que a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>foi occupying.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [recursos não geridos limpeza](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método eliminar](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada `Dispose` antes de libertar a última referência <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está a utilizar não irão ser libertados até que as chamadas de recoletor de lixo a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Liberta os recursos não geridos utilizados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider"> </xref> e opcionalmente liberta os recursos geridos.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Para libertar recursos geridos e; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> para libertar recursos apenas não geridos.

trans-unit.source: Returns all exports that match the conditions of the specified import.
trans-unit.target: Devolve todas as exportações que correspondam às condições da importação especificada.

trans-unit.source: Implementers should not treat cardinality-related mismatches as errors and should not throw exceptions for cardinality-related mismatches.
trans-unit.target: Os implementadores não devem tratar relacionadas com cardinalidade correspondência como erros e não devem acionar exceções para relacionadas com a cardinalidade de correspondência.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the import requests exactly one export and the provider has either no matching exports or more than one, the GetExportsCore method should return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> objects.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se a importação pedidos exatamente uma exportação e o fornecedor tem não exporta correspondente ou mais do que um, o método GetExportsCore deverá devolver vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>coleção de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>objetos.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>
